Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.80,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HC43F20&\bord2\blur3\pos(780,660)}绝不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:58.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(850,430)}简直{\c&H3EE1D9&}糟透了
